Package cscie97.asn1.knowledge.engine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Importer
    Loads new Triples from an input file into the KnowledgeGraph.
    KnowledgeGraph
    An in-memory database of Triples, which allows for the importation of new Triples into the database as well as queries on the database and returns matching Triples.
    Node
    Represents a Node, which is part of a Triple.
    Predicate
    Represents a Predicate, which is part of a Triple.
    QueryEngine
    Used to execute queries against the KnowledgeGraph for matching Triples.
    Triple
    Represents a Triple, which is comprised of a "subject" (a Node), a Predicate, and an "object" (another Node).
